[Although we know the number of "fatal cases", we have yet to hear how many
have been confirmed as having been due to JE virus infection. I would hate
to think that all these efforts, all this money, and all this time is being
spent on JE virus eradication when the epidemic is either of mixed etiology
or principally due to something other than JE virus. I suppose we will
know soon. - Mod.CHC
